name: ao_documentation_maker
description: Just starting point....will see yet what will become out of it.

scripts._install: bash -c " git clone https://github.com/MyUserNameIsMyUserName/A-O_builder-express.git  && echo |bash A-O_builder-express/ao_builder/install.sh && cd  A-O_builder-express && npm install && cd .. && echo $PWD && cp -r A-O_builder-express/node_modules/ ./  && cp  A-O_builder-express/ao_express.js ./ "
scripts._uninstall: bash -c " rm -r  A-O_builder-express -f && rm -r node_modules -f && rm -r PUBLIC -f && rm ao_express.js "
scripts._build_and_run: npm run b_ && start node ao_express.js
